        content: `<p>Nixxon Australia reserves the right to request the removal of links to our website and amend these terms and conditions and linking policies. Continued linking implies agreement to abide by these terms.</p>`,
    },
    {
        title: "23. Removal of Links",
        content: `<p>If you find any offensive links, please inform us. We may consider requests to remove links but are not obligated to respond directly.</p>
